WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:02:49.800 --> 00:03:20.640
Take about 80 gr of white soap base and 
put it in a glass.

00:03:20.640 --> 00:03:34.880
Take about 20 gr of vegetable butter coconut and 
put it in a glass, too. Then cliff bain-marie or
melt in microwave.

00:03:34.880 --> 00:04:00.000
Put it in a silicone mold.

00:04:00.000 --> 00:04:24.960
Add add 1 \ 2 tbsp coconut flour. 
Then mix.

00:04:24.960 --> 00:04:47.640
Mix to avoid that the coconut flour remains 
on the bottom of the mold.

00:04:47.640 --> 00:05:12.600
Then remove them from the mold.

00:05:12.600 --> 00:05:28.880
Preserve them in plastic wrap.

00:05:28.880 --> 00:06:14.560
Pack with (for example) transparent paper 
and colored ribbon, as shown in the video.

